            android:text="During the conference, you will wear a sensing deviceâ€“ the E4 wristband by Empatica. The device will collect data about your blood pressure, galvanic skin response and skin temperature. This sensor data will give us an objective basis to understand your level of engagement/attention/interest during the presentations. You will also be asked to rank the papers of the conference and fill-in short questionnaires via Energieinformatik17 Android application. Your answers will allow us to gather information on your opinion about the presentation. You can refrain from answering any question you might prefer not to answer (e.g., because it makes you uncomfortable) and you can stop the survey at any time."
